video.title: Spirit Riding Free
video.synopsis: In a small Western town, spunky ex-city girl Lucky forms a tight bond with wild horse Spirit while having adventures with best pals Pru and Abigail.

episodes.synopsis: Newly arrived in the town of Miradero, city girl Lucky struggles to fit in at school but befriends a wild stallion after he is wrangled for taming.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Unbreakable Spirit

episodes.synopsis: Headstrong Lucky persuades Pru to give her a crash course in horseback riding so she and Spirit can participate in the annual Saddle Club race.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Treacherous Trail

episodes.synopsis: On her first camping trip, Lucky decides to decode her dad's old treasure map, then sneaks off with Abigail, Pru and Spirit to find the fortune.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Mysterious Map

episodes.synopsis: Desperate to be Student of the Month, Lucky teams with Maricela to create a booth for a school fundraiser, pitting herself against Pru and Abigail.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Competition Conundrum

episodes.synopsis: As Lucky and saddlemaker Turo plot to help a horse neglected by his cruel owner, Lucky's dad works to fix a cracked dam before disaster strikes.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Appaloosa Adventure

episodes.synopsis: Determined to throw Pru the best surprise birthday party ever, Lucky enlists Abigail's help in planning the event, which quickly gets out of hand.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Not-So-Secret Surprise

episodes.synopsis: Eager to follow in her mother's footsteps, Lucky gets lessons in trick riding from dashing young performer Javier.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Cowboy Next Door

episodes.synopsis: When Abigail's prize cherry pie goes missing, Lucky draws inspiration from her favorite book sleuth and plays detective with her pals.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Pie P.I.

episodes.synopsis: Lucky's visiting cousin, Julian, charms her friends with his exciting schemes, but Lucky worries that he's up to no good.
episodes.title: Lucky and Her Super Amazing and Fun Cousin Julian

episodes.synopsis: At the harvest scavenger hunt, Julian bets a day of chores that he and the other boys will find the scarecrow prize before Lucky and the other girls.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Harvest Hunt

episodes.synopsis: When a blizzard threatens to derail the town's Christmas celebrations, Lucky and her pals organize a secret "Santa's elves" gift-giving campaign.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Christmas Spirit

episodes.synopsis: Lucky and Maricela join forces when a train carrying flu medicine crashes during a blizzard and they're the only ones healthy enough to help.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Deadly Blizzard

episodes.synopsis: Determined to join a men-only horse race, Lucky poses as a man. But with vicious Grayson as her main rival, the contest soon takes a dangerous turn.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Price of Freedom

episodes.synopsis: Spirit's a wild stallion, but he can't bear the thought of being away from Lucky -- which means he'll do anything to find his way back home.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Long Way Home

episodes.synopsis: As a mare in Spirit's herd prepares to give birth, Lucky enrolls Pru and Abigail in Prescott's Charm School to get them ready for the Governor's Ball.
episodes.title: Lucky and the New Governor

episodes.synopsis: The girls plan a risky mission to free a wrongly detained Tuckapaw teen from a speeding train and reunite him with his trusty horse.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Risky Rescue

episodes.synopsis: After the kids at school tease her about being "teacher's pet," Lucky sets out to prove them wrong by stirring up trouble on an overnight field trip.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Field Trip Fraud

episodes.synopsis: When a rumbling earthquake takes out a railroad bridge, Lucky and her friends must find a way to warn the passengers aboard a fast-approaching train.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Shaky Day

episodes.synopsis: A potentially big payoff goes off the rails when Lucky and her pals find gold and enlist the help of Lucky's crafty cousin, Julian.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Golden Opportunity

episodes.synopsis: Lucky and the girls help Aunt Cora back into the saddle to prepare for an upcoming ride. A mountain lion threatens Spirit's herd.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Lion

episodes.synopsis: While Spirit heals from an injury, Lucky assists a sidelined Winthrop at his store by dishing up ice cream -- and advice -- with mixed results.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Impatient Patient

episodes.synopsis: Lucky's over the moon about the O-Mok-See she has planned for her 13th birthday ... until her wealthy grandpa rolls into town with his own ideas.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Train Tycoon

episodes.synopsis: Lucky and her dad are doing their best to keep things running smoothly at home. But everything's a disaster without Aunt Cora -- even the school play!
episodes.title: Lucky and the Role Reversal

episodes.synopsis: Lucky's so desperate to stop Aunt Cora from leaving Miradero that she'll stoop to anything (even goosenapping!) to keep her in town.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Patchwork Plan

episodes.synopsis: Miss Flores feels out of place when a traveling circus brings Lucky closer to her mother than ever before. A rival horse steps up to challenge Spirit.
episodes.title: Lucky and Her New Family Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Lucky's proud to follow in her mother's footsteps when a young circus star can't perform. But it feels like her father's putting Miss Flores first.
episodes.title: Lucky and Her New Family Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After learning Lucky's run off to join the circus, Pru and Abigail set out to find their friend and bring her back home.
episodes.title: Lucky and La Voltereta Feroz

episodes.synopsis: Lucky vows to protect her circus family from a shadowy bandit on the loose. Meanwhile, Pru conquers her stage fright -- and finds her calling.
episodes.title: Lucky and the No-Good Outlaw Butch LePray

episodes.synopsis: When the troupe stops in a town that doesn't trust circus folk, Lucky and her friends stage a secret performance for the kids who can't see the show.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Big Goodbye

episodes.synopsis: The PALs return to big changes in Miradero, and one of the biggest is Maricela ... on a bicycle! Later, Lucky gives Miss Flores some riding tips.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Two-Wheeled Terror

episodes.synopsis: Luckys dying for a little excitement when Pru's dad invites the PALs on a real-live mustang drive. But she gets way more than she wanted!
episodes.title: Lucky and the Rough Ride

episodes.synopsis: Lucky and her friends are getting older. So instead of trick-or-treating, they come up with an elaborate plan to scare Snips for Halloween.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Ghostly Gotcha!

episodes.synopsis: A PALs adventure takes a dangerous turn when the girls try to deliver a returned wedding invitation to the orphanage where Miss Flores grew up.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Doomed Delivery

episodes.synopsis: When hot times hit Miradero, every well in town dries up -- except for Grayson's. So where's he getting his water? The PALs hatch a plan to find out.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Doubtful Drought

episodes.synopsis: Pru's in charge while her dad is away, and she's desperate to prove she's responsible. Aunt Cora helps Kate find the perfect wedding dress.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Arabian Nightmares

episodes.synopsis: The PALs are determined to become official Frontier Fillies. But Snips -- and a dangerous dust storm -- will put all their skills to the test.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Fearless Fillies

episodes.synopsis: Lucky's got a list of New Year's resolutions -- and only one day left to complete them! Cue an old friend riding into town with a big surprise.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Resolutionary Fever

episodes.synopsis: Lucky convinces her cousin's friends that her house holds a set of shrunken heads. Kate gives Lucky a special gift before the wedding.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Cousin Caper

episodes.synopsis: Everything's going wrong on wedding day, and it seems like the big day is cursed. Can Lucky and her friends save Jim and Kate from disaster?
episodes.title: Lucky and the Wayward Wedding

episodes.synopsis: While a patient Kate waits at the altar, Spirit and the PALs spring into action to stop a speeding train -- with support from a surprising ally.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Railroad Ransom

episodes.synopsis: Lucky's scheming cousin, Julian, is up to his old tricks when he goes to the city to find his future and comes back with a hot air balloon.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Flight of the Fancy

episodes.synopsis: April Fools' Day begins with Lucky and her friends playing pranks on all their classmates. But it ends with a very big surprise!
episodes.title: Lucky and the Jam Jam

episodes.synopsis: Lucky's so eager to prove she's responsible that she volunteers to be Snips's big sister for the day. After all, how hard could it be?
episodes.title: Lucky and the Escape Artist

episodes.synopsis: Snowy tracks point the PALs to an injured traveler -- and the realization that he wasn't alone. Can they find his young daughter before it's too late?
episodes.title: Lucky and the Thin Ice

episodes.synopsis: After the PALs accidentally break Grayson's window, Abigail's determined to turn him into a friend. But he doesn't seem to want any part of it.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Ray of Sunshine

episodes.synopsis: To help their daughters become full-fledged Frontier Fillies, Jim and Al design an obstacle course that puts all of the PALs' skills to the test.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Double-Dad Dare

episodes.synopsis: When a huge storm sparks danger for a wild herd, Jim and Spirit ride off to the rescue, leaving a very pregnant Kate in Lucky's care.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Warm Welcome

episodes.synopsis: A confident Pru can't wait to prove herself in the ring at a prestigious riding competition. But Lucky's convinced someone's setting her up to lose.
episodes.title: Lucky and the Dressage Sabotage

episodes.synopsis: The PALs team up to take care of Lucky's new baby sister, Polly -- and an adorable wolf cub they found in the wild. What could possibly go wrong?
episodes.title: Lucky and the Girl Who Cried Wolf

episodes.synopsis: A career day at school finds Lucky and her friends shadowing adults with interesting jobs. But Lucky has so many passions, it's hard to pick just one!
episodes.title: Lucky and the Endless Possibilities

episodes.synopsis: First impressions are everything at a big-city interview that could make or break Lucky's chances of going to boarding school.
episodes.title: Lucky and the New Frontier: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The PALs pack their belongings and prepare to leave Miradero behind. But is Spirit coming along for the ride ... or staying home?
episodes.title: Lucky and the New Frontier: Part 2
